Internal announcement
———
Attention: Handle your freedom with care

This is not a pressure for anyone specific, it's more of a reminder to everyone as whole.

We understand that our companies aren't the company which paying the highest salary/income but we believe that we are among the free (freedom) company out there. And if you work here in one of the project, we expect that you sign up for the challenge that our companies is facing, together.  



---note---
In the time crisis and economic turmoil, everything is tough. We understand that some people may have personal problems at home that may effect their work at the company. If this is the case, come forth and tell one of us or during the meeting, if we you comfortable and if you think our team can do something to help.

